A whimsical Studio Ghibli-style illustration of a colossal, gentle deity figure sitting cross-legged on clouds, examining a transparent human anatomical model held delicately in enormous hands. The figure wears a hard hat and tool belt overflowing with unusual instruments—wrenches, circuit boards, beakers, and blueprints. Around them float semi-transparent overlays showing different body systems: glowing neural pathways like golden lightning, mechanical joint diagrams with gears, flowing rivers of crimson representing circulation, and architectural scaffolding along the spine. The background features a soft sunset sky in peach and lavender tones, with floating islands containing miniature construction projects. The deity's expression is one of bemused contemplation, perhaps noticing a design flaw. Soft, painterly brushstrokes with warm lighting characteristic of Japanese animation, featuring rich details and a sense of wonder and gentle humor.
